<div class="user-wrapper text-center">
  <div class="confirmation-icon mb-4">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check" style="font-size: 4rem; color: #28a745;"></i>
  </div>

  <h1>Thanks for your inquiry!</h1>

  <div class="alert alert-success mt-4">
    <p class="mb-0"><strong>We've received your commercial collection inquiry.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4">
    <p>We'll review your requirements and get in touch within <strong>1-2 business days</strong> to discuss:</p>
    <ul class="text-start" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <li>Customized pricing for your needs</li>
      <li>Collection schedule and logistics</li>
      <li>Contract details and next steps</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4">
    <p>In the meantime, check your email for a confirmation message.</p>
    <p>If you have urgent questions, feel free to call us directly.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5">
    <%= link_to "Return to Home", root_path, class: "btn-gooi" %>
  </div>
</div>
